title: Legislative Service Bureau, State Senate District Boundaries, Iowa, 1992 - 2001
name: Legislative Service Bureau, State Senate District Boundaries, Iowa, 1992 - 2001
description:
Abstract:

This coverage contains polygons representing the Iowa Senate district boundaries for 1992-2001.

Purpose:

This digital, geographically referenced data set was developed by the Iowa Department of Natural Resources to carry out agency responsibilities related to management, protection, and development of Iowa's natural resources
